## Someday/Maybe
- [ ] **Create Weekly Review Template in Obsidian** ^task-20260216-001
	- Create an Obsidian template for weekly review workflow:
- Review This Week (15 min) - calendar, meetings, commitments
- System Health Check (5 min) - task counts, priority balance
- Plan Next Week (10 min) - preview calendar, set priorities
- Triage & Clean Up (10 min) - archive, reassign priorities
- Document (5 min) - learnings, carry-overs

Template should use work-mcp tools: get_week_progress, get_system_status, check_goal_alignment

Effort: ~15-20 minutes
Benefit: Systematic weekly planning, prevents work overflow
	- Pillar: Personal/Hobbies | Priority: P3


